{"type": "article", "id": 16404, "title": "空无一人时的俄罗斯地铁，华丽程度让人惊讶", "description": "“我真不是故意在为俄罗斯地铁打广告”，摄影师 David Burdeny 说，“它们实在是太美了。”", "date": "2015-10-22T06:03:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 373, "name": "俄罗斯"}, {"id": 887, "name": "地铁"}, {"id": 17591, "name": "华丽"}, {"id": 7319, "name": "摄影师"}, {"id": 17592, "name": "David Burdeny"}], "genre": 1, "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134401K49DuGSf6Ui0oOLX.png", "contents": "\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t每一天，每一年，在北京、纽约、伦敦、莫斯科、东京等国际都市的地铁里，有成千上万的人匆匆穿行。其中，莫斯科的地铁以最为富丽堂皇而闻名，乍一走进这些地铁站，你会误以为自己进入了皇宫或博物馆，繁复华丽的装饰、考究的细节，它们穿越了时代，兀自地美着，完全不 care 现代社会发生着什么。但习惯了在莫斯科生活的人，可能很少留心这些细节。最近，摄影师<a href=\"http://davidburdeny.com\" target=\"_blank\"> David Burdeny </a>在莫斯科的 200 个地铁车站里选出了 30 个，并给它们拍了照片，<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3052432/exposure/enter-the-ornate-world-of-russias-underground-stations#14\" target=\"_blank\">集合成的影集叫作 A Bright Future </a>，“我真不是故意在为俄罗斯地铁打广告”，这位摄影师说，“它们实在是太美了。”\r\n</p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\"Elektrozavodskaya Station, 莫斯科，俄罗斯 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134349Wgly3zK1PjxJfGC7.jpg-w600\" title=\"Elektrozavodskaya Station, 莫斯科，俄罗斯 2015\" width=\"640\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<span>Elektrozavodskaya Station, Moscow , Russia , 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">每个车站都由俄罗斯著名建筑师设计，有不同的风格，建筑结构也不同：</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Kiyevsskaya 东站, 俄罗斯莫斯科 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134349eaXtqmJHW2BNdyMo.jpg-w600\" title=\"Kiyevsskaya 东站, 俄罗斯莫斯科 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Kiyevsskaya  2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Kiyevsskaya Station，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134350GEiBCAO6yfZ7s3Hj.jpg-w600\" title=\"Kiyevsskaya Station，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Kiyevsskaya Station , 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Komsomolskaya 站，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134351EIFDr1pzGwRvL6kX.jpg-w600\" title=\"Komsomolskaya 站，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Komsomolskaya , 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Kropotkinskaya ，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134352YR8EGc9WjSUsozOF.jpg-w600\" title=\"Kropotkinskaya ，俄罗斯莫斯科，2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Kropotkinskaya , 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Mayakovskaya Station, Moscow, Russia, 2014\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134353PpKikRrq7hu8Geaw.jpg-w600\" title=\"Mayakovskaya Station, Moscow, Russia, 2014\" width=\"640\"/><span>Mayakovskaya Station, Moscow, Russia, 2014</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Novocherkasskaya Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134354Dpn20AF1VN7cLZIq.jpg-w600\" title=\"Novocherkasskaya Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014\" width=\"640\"/><span>Novocherkasskaya Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Arbatskaya Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134354KHVG2gWmIXwB3xPR.jpg-w600\" title=\"Arbatskaya Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Arbatskaya Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Sokol Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134356le1HP0Dq457Xtfb9.jpg-w600\" title=\"Sokol Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/>Sokol Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\r\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Aeroport Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/201607021343571uy8zr2iMYZ9Fmht.jpg-w600\" title=\"Aeroport Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/>Aeroport Metro Station, Moscow, Russia, 2015\r\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Avoto Metro Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/2016070213435862iYZkourUD3VO9C.jpg-w600\" title=\"Avoto Metro Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014\" width=\"640\"/>Avoto Metro Station, St Petersburg, Russia, 2014<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Red Wall, Peterhof, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/201607021343589y5wD4zFMujAa1qO.jpg-w600\" title=\"Red Wall, Peterhof, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Red Wall, Peterhof, Russia, 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Winter Red, Catherine Palace, Pushkin, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134359bDwWqdVlYhrQZ2Ee.jpg-w600\" title=\"Winter Red, Catherine Palace, Pushkin, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Winter Red, Catherine Palace, Pushkin, Russia, 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t拍摄这些照片并非易事，David Burdeny 一直试图打通官僚上的繁文缛节，但都没什么进展。后来他偶然认识了 Top Gear 的制片人，这个英国节目曾在莫斯科的地铁里拍摄取景。在这位制片人的帮助下，David Burdeny 得以用两周的时间去拍摄这些车站，每个车站的拍摄时间是一小时。\r\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<span>下面是俄罗斯的一些宫殿或博物馆：</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Blue Drawing Room. Catherine Palace. Pushkin, Russia, 2014\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/201607021343596mkYJRyHOxgSzT0i.jpg-w600\" title=\"Blue Drawing Room. Catherine Palace. Pushkin, Russia, 2014\" width=\"640\"/><span>Blue Drawing Room. Catherine Palace. Pushkin, Russia, 2014</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Docent I, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134400tv8BqHuxE7ngMkrS.jpg-w600\" title=\"Docent I, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Docent I, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<img alt=\"Docent II, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015\" class=\"\" data-format=\"jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://img.qdaily.com/uploads/20160702134401jQCp7bS1gLEilTtn.jpg-w600\" title=\"Docent II, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015\" width=\"640\"/><span>Docent II, State Hemitage, St Petersburg, Russia, 2015</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t其实莫斯科地铁是世界上规模最大的地铁系统之一，它还是世界上使用效率第二高的地下轨道系统（第一是纽约）。地铁一期工程动工于 1935 年，当时苏联政府建造地铁是出于军事方面的考虑，<span style=\"text-align:left;\">地铁可供 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">400 余万居民掩蔽防护之用</span>。另外<span style=\"text-align:left;\">斯大林希望把莫斯科打造为无产阶级的新罗马，地铁也就成为了意识形态的宣传工具，因此设计得富丽堂皇。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span>\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n</div>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n</p>\n<p>\n<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3052432/exposure/enter-the-ornate-world-of-russias-underground-stations#11\" target=\"_blank\"><em>fastcodesign</em></a>\n</p>\n"}